Class PlanTableEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.matching.single.cypher.planning.plantable.PlanTableEntry

  • public class PlanTableEntry
extends Object
    Represents a query plan and additional meta data. Plan table entries are managed in a PlanTable.
